{"hfd5e826ag62eag4799ga818gc1b275653bca": ["For the Absolute!", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "88c74525-27fb-745e-244f-3e57c84e7e3c"], "h183d6b43g4c4dg4e21ga77egbe096c1255b2": ["... an' the gnoll gnawed 'er arm clean off. So much for the Flamin' Fist, eh?", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "e8b0013d-2560-5443-4185-c0179f456b0e"], "h55e8bef9g9045g4242gb5e9gf2920b76fac9": ["Sounds like a bloody scrap. Where did you see that?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "44c3c67c-acf2-997c-ac78-5f173def5fc4"], "h79c957eag29d1g44e8gb56fge38c09e23583": ["You ain't hear? We sacked Waukeen's Rest and left it to <i>burn.</i>", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "3fe72392-bda8-c949-7ff2-934e33c16712"], "h294b07abg97e8g48c3gba5ag728fd8d0bf62": ["Drow flingin' magic, gnolls snappin' off heads. Inn's nothin' but a pile of ash by now.", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "5c41aca2-4044-1af3-112e-6a2bb31005f3"], "h0996d16dge713g469eg988bgbfe4fd8fa6f4": ["<i>Glorious.</i>", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "4df576f0-ebfc-61d1-4578-9280436b2fba"], "h7066456fgd667g4d6bga402gb3436ff66084": ["What's a Flaming Fist?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "450e3e3c-94d4-c7d7-c324-b30bf1777d9c"], "h2fe4e47cgd4f7g4692g8b0cgf5af70527a3e": ["The Fist? Merc pigs from Baldur's Gate. Good for one thing: feedin' to worgs.", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "52fd1d05-e406-cbc0-e13b-5c29d423b206"], "h0d59a1e0g497fg4dc4g815fg634498eee38d": ["You saw a Flaming Fist? Where?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "d7748ba0-94aa-ca2d-3e1d-0f6c07312d93"], "h7ac8d764g4eccg4083gab30g9a99bf4c808a": ["Were there any survivors?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "d9571bdb-5bbd-9e3b-b0e0-6fdd769d3477"], "hbab5eb22g6ed0g45eagbd5dg8cca409f251c": ["Buncha prisoners got towed to Moonrise. City snobs, mostly.", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "7cfaedff-5ccd-8e5d-6df2-0a7fe3e94beb"], "h517cc74eg8640g427fgac49g20986f9e24e8": ["But the Flamin' Fist? Pile of smokin' corpses.", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "164ddd5d-8483-f83f-cf54-13a632a9713d"], "h270b7b1ege0b7g48a6gbbecg8216d59f4906": ["Do you happen to know the way to Moonrise?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "f7ad1b39-0595-0e7c-4fbc-0e480b0edb65"], "hfb5d3ab2gf1d6g4e35gb4d9g44586f305545": ["I figgered a drow would know the broken road!", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "96c34439-8d27-63e5-1204-578ee1a85ff7"], "h6c5956e8g083cg46c4ga6fbg7f0445f7a00b": ["An under-dwarf ain't know the broken road? Heh!", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "96c34439-8d27-63e5-1204-578ee1a85ff7"], "he51e8062ga979g4db9g883eg1644b6af72df": ["You ain't know the broken road? Heh!", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "96c34439-8d27-63e5-1204-578ee1a85ff7"], "hed89a909gc136g42b3g9f30gae54480b18f6": ["Take the north path. It winds ya 'round, sure as sunshine, till you reach the towers.", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "79ff694c-72cf-6421-223b-5e92e0a7b1a0"], "ha8bb6920g37d2g41e8gacaag94b644c4fcc7": ["I'll tell ya real slow-like so ya don't miss it:", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "dbf847d1-fe1b-d93a-ff95-324f5443b971"], "h4f991566gdaa3g4505g9e99gd318e23e481c": ["<i>North.</i>", "c7e85da4-2100-4d25-9a54-8feb5edbbb14", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "80116aa4-39d7-7de5-161a-9da011e345a3"], "h9157ed54g76c9g4e0ag87b5gb054c7934952": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_Backup002.html", "55c169be-06d1-6356-e2c7-05731ae9dabd"]}